episodes.title: The Lost Boys of the Cedu School/Cult
episodes.description:
Blake Pursley,  Daniel Yuen and John Inman all disappeared while residents at a controversial California camp known as The Cedu School.
Touted as a "therapeutic boarding school for troubled youth" 
But residents say it was an abusive cult and a place of child endangerment.
What happened to the three young men who went missing from the Cedu School?
Were they the only ones?
Did the police keep secrets?
